Package: ScuRMST
Title: Two Stages Double-arm Clinical Trial Design Using Sculpted Critical Region of RMST
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Jiashan", family = "He", email = "gaaisin@connect.hku.hk", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This package is for Sculpted RMST Two Stages Double-arm Clinical Trial Design. 
    Sculpted refers to a defined critical region that necessitates both a significant difference in RMST 
    between groups and a large absolute value of RMST in the experimental group in order to declare the treatment effective.
